creator: Sa Zu
descriptionHtml:
An easy-to-integrate mail service has been created to meet all your needs so you can easily manage your mailboxes using our website, API or mobile application.

APP Features:
-Sync your mailboxes with your mobile phone using our app. First you will need to choose the mailboxes you want to sync with your mobile phone from your account page.
-Create random or customized mailboxes with custom duration with a few clicks.
-Remove any mailbox with one click.
-Whether a mailbox is in sync mode or not, you can get all the messages using the token assigned to each mailbox.
-Receive new messages on your phone, delete or send these messages.
-Write and send messages. If you are a registered user and have private domains, you can easily send custom messages from your domain to anyone.
-If you don't have private domains, you can test the service using the Free Package which allow you to create and manage temporary mailboxes.
descriptionShort: SpectreMail is a service to manage your mails and messages with minimal effort
